data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bed, 2 bath Stonybrooke subdivision home in sought after North Richland Hills! Tremendous curb appeal coupled with an abundance of windows allow for tons of natural light throughout! Almost every room has been upgraded with add'tl home amenities including hardwoods, brand new master bed, subtle grey paint tones & updated bath! The kitchen with island includes granite counters, tile back-splash & SS appliances. Large master includes views of yard & has en-suite bath with separate tub, stand-in shower & dual sinks. All add'tl beds include hardwoods & spacious in size! Enjoy the Texas weather outdoors with the covered & open patio & oversized garden area! 3D model & walk thru available!
